<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0, maximum-scale=1.0, user-scalable=no">
    <title>Nexra Screen Recorder | Studio Quality. Zero Latency.</title>
    <meta name="description" content="A premium, privacy-centric browser-based screen recording suite with 4K support, real-time audio mixing, and invisible watermarking.">
    <link rel="icon" type="image/png" href="https://uploads.onecompiler.io/42yatf6fu/1781258941988/25088C4A-230C-4E61-8E84-C40FD3A6033C-removebg-preview.png">
    <meta name="theme-color" content="#000000">

    <!-- 
    ===========================================================================
    PRODUCT REQUIREMENTS DOCUMENT (PRD) - NEXRA SCREEN RECORDER
    ===========================================================================
    Product Vision: A premium SaaS interface inspired by VisionOS and OBS. No server-side video processing. 
    Design System: Pure Black (#000000), Slate (#0F0F11), Nexra Orange (#FF5A00). Liquid glass overlays.
    Features Built-in:
    1. Local-First Processing (WebRTC, MediaRecorder).
    2. OBS-Style Capture (Screen, Tab, Window, PiP Webcam with shapes/blur/mirror).
    3. Advanced Audio (System + Mic mixing, visual meter, noise reduction).
    4. Smart Tools (7s Countdown, Auto-stop, Shortcuts).
    5. In-Recording Annotations (Pen, Arrow, Highlighter, Blur sensitive info).
    6. Watermark Engine: Invisible during recording -> Burned into MP4 via Canvas during Export.
    7. PWA Ready: Offline capable via Service Workers.
    8. Firebase Auth & Sync: Guest access allowed; auth forced ONLY on export. Syncs settings to Firestore.
    
    Firestore Security Rules Required:
    rules_version = '2';
    service cloud.firestore {
      match /databases/{database}/documents {
        match /users/{userId} {
          allow read, write: if request.auth != null && request.auth.uid == userId;
        }
      }
    }
    ===========================================================================
    -->

    <style>
        /* --- DESIGN SYSTEM & CSS VARIABLES --- */
        :root {
            --black: #000000;
            --slate: #0F0F11;
            --slate-light: #1A1A1E;
            --orange: #FF5A00;
            --orange-glow: rgba(255, 90, 0, 0.4);
            --white: #FFFFFF;
            --text-muted: #888888;
            --glass-bg: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.03);
            --glass-border: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
            --font-main: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
            --z-header: 1000;
            --z-modal: 2000;
            --z-pip: 500;
            --z-toast: 3000;
        }

        /* --- RESETS & BASE --- */
        * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; font-family: var(--font-main); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; }
        body { background-color: var(--black); color: var(--white); overflow-x: hidden; scroll-behavior: smooth; }
        ::-webkit-scrollbar { width: 6px; height: 6px; }
        ::-webkit-scrollbar-track { background: transparent; }
        ::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb { background: var(--glass-border); border-radius: 10px; }
        ::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb:hover { background: var(--orange); }

        /* --- GLASSMORPHISM UTILITIES --- */
        .liquid-glass {
            background: rgba(15, 15, 17, 0.6);
            backdrop-filter: blur(24px);
            -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(24px);
            border-bottom: 1px solid var(--glass-border);
        }
        .frosted-panel {
            background: var(--glass-bg);
            backdrop-filter: blur(16px);
            -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(16px);
            border: 1px solid var(--glass-border);
            border-radius: 16px;
            box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
            transition: all 0.3s cubic-bezier(0.25, 0.8, 0.25, 1);
        }
        .frosted-panel:hover {
            border-color: rgba(255, 90, 0, 0.3);
            box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(255, 90, 0, 0.1);
        }

        /* --- TYPOGRAPHY & BUTTONS --- */
        h1, h2, h3 { font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: -0.02em; }
        .text-gradient {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--white) 0%, var(--text-muted) 100%);
            -webkit-background-clip: text; -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
        }
        .text-orange { color: var(--orange); }
        
        .btn {
            display: inline-flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; gap: 8px;
            padding: 12px 24px; border-radius: 12px; font-weight: 600; cursor: pointer;
            transition: all 0.2s ease; border: none; outline: none; font-size: 14px;
        }
        .btn-primary {
            background: var(--orange); color: var(--white);
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px var(--orange-glow);
        }
        .btn-primary:hover { transform: translateY(-2px); box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(255, 90, 0, 0.6); }
        .btn-primary:active { transform: translateY(0); }
        .btn-glass { background: var(--glass-bg); border: 1px solid var(--glass-border); color: var(--white); }
        .btn-glass:hover { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.08); border-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.2); }
        
        .icon-btn {
            background: transparent; border: 1px solid transparent; color: var(--white);
            padding: 10px; border-radius: 50%; cursor: pointer; transition: all 0.2s; display: flex;
        }
        .icon-btn:hover { background: var(--glass-bg); border-color: var(--glass-border); color: var(--orange); }
        .icon-btn.active { color: var(--orange); background: rgba(255, 90, 0, 0.1); border-color: var(--orange); }

        /* --- HEADER --- */
        header { position: sticky; top: 0; width: 100%; z-index: var(--z-header); display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; padding: 16px 5%; }
        .logo { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 12px; font-size: 20px; font-weight: 700; cursor: pointer; }
        .logo img { width: 32px; height: 32px; object-fit: contain; }
        
        /* --- LAYOUTS --- */
        .view-section { display: none; min-height: calc(100vh - 70px); width: 100%; padding: 40px 5%; animation: fadeIn 0.4s ease forwards; }
        .view-section.active { display: block; }
        
        /* Landing */
        #landing-page { text-align: center; padding-top: 100px; }
        #landing-page h1 { font-size: clamp(40px, 6vw, 72px); margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.1; }
        #landing-page p { font-size: 20px; color: var(--text-muted); max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto 40px; }
        
        /* Dashboard */
        .dashboard-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 300px 1fr; gap: 30px; height: calc(100vh - 150px); }
        .sidebar { padding: 24px; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 20px; }
        .menu-item { padding: 12px 16px; border-radius: 8px; cursor: pointer; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 12px; color: var(--text-muted); transition: 0.2s; }
        .menu-item:hover, .menu-item.active { background: var(--glass-bg); color: var(--white); border-left: 3px solid var(--orange); }
        
        /* Studio */
        .studio-container { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 20px; height: calc(100vh - 120px); }
        .preview-wrapper { flex: 1; position: relative; background: var(--slate); border-radius: 16px; overflow: hidden; border: 1px solid var(--glass-border); display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; }
        #screen-preview { width: 100%; height: 100%; object-fit: contain; }
        #annotation-canvas { position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%; pointer-events: none; z-index: 10; }
        .controls-bar { padding: 16px 24px; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; gap: 20px; }
        
        /* PiP Camera */
        .pip-container {
            position: absolute; bottom: 30px; right: 30px; width: 200px; height: 200px; 
            z-index: var(--z-pip); cursor: grab; overflow: hidden; box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.8);
            transition: border-radius 0.3s ease; border: 2px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
        }
        .pip-container:active { cursor: grabbing; }
        .pip-container.shape-circle { border-radius: 50%; }
        .pip-container.shape-square { border-radius: 8px; }
        .pip-container.shape-rect { width: 260px; height: 160px; border-radius: 12px; }
        .pip-container video { width: 100%; height: 100%; object-fit: cover; transform: scaleX(-1); /* default mirror */ }
        .pip-container.blur-bg { filter: drop-shadow(0 0 10px var(--orange)); }
        
        /* Audio Meter */
        .audio-meter { display: flex; gap: 4px; align-items: center; height: 20px; }
        .meter-bar { width: 4px; height: 4px; background: var(--glass-border); border-radius: 2px; transition: height 0.1s, background 0.1s; }
        
        /* Countdown Overlay */
        #countdown-overlay { position: fixed; inset: 0; background: rgba(0,0,0,0.8); backdrop-filter: blur(10px); z-index: 9999; display: none; align-items: center; justify-content: center; flex-direction: column; }
        #countdown-number { font-size: 150px; font-weight: 800; color: var(--orange); animation: pulseScale 1s infinite; }

        /* Modals */
        .modal-overlay { position: fixed; inset: 0; background: rgba(0,0,0,0.8); backdrop-filter: blur(10px); z-index: var(--z-modal); display: none; align-items: center; justify-content: center; opacity: 0; transition: opacity 0.3s; }
        .modal-overlay.active { display: flex; opacity: 1; }
        .modal-content { width: 100%; max-width: 400px; padding: 32px; position: relative; transform: translateY(20px); transition: transform 0.3s; }
        .modal-overlay.active .modal-content { transform: translateY(0); }
        .form-group { margin-bottom: 20px; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 8px; }
        .form-group label { font-size: 13px; color: var(--text-muted); }
        .form-control { width: 100%; padding: 14px; background: var(--slate-light); border: 1px solid var(--glass-border); border-radius: 10px; color: var(--white); outline: none; transition: 0.2s; }
        .form-control:focus { border-color: var(--orange); box-shadow: 0 0 0 2px var(--orange-glow); }
        
        /* Toast */
        #toast-container { position: fixed; bottom: 30px; left: 50%; transform: translateX(-50%); z-index: var(--z-toast); display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 10px; }
        .toast { padding: 12px 24px; background: rgba(255, 90, 0, 0.9); backdrop-filter: blur(10px); color: white; border-radius: 30px; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 500; animation: slideUpToast 0.4s ease forwards; }

        /* Utilities */
        .hidden { display: none !important; }
        .flex { display: flex; }
        .gap-2 { gap: 8px; }
        .gap-4 { gap: 16px; }

        /* Animations */
        @keyframes fadeIn { from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(10px); } to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); } }
        @keyframes pulseScale { 0% { transform: scale(0.8); opacity: 0.5; } 50% { transform: scale(1.2); opacity: 1; } 100% { transform: scale(0.8); opacity: 0.5; } }
        @keyframes slideUpToast { from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(20px); } to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); } }
        
        /* Export Progress */
        .progress-bar-bg { width: 100%; height: 8px; background: var(--slate-light); border-radius: 4px; overflow: hidden; margin-top: 10px; }
        .progress-bar-fill { height: 100%; width: 0%; background: var(--orange); box-shadow: 0 0 10px var(--orange); transition: width 0.2s linear; }

        /* Responsive */
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .dashboard-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
            .sidebar { flex-direction: row; overflow-x: auto; padding: 16px; }
            .controls-bar { flex-wrap: wrap; justify-content: center; }
            .pip-container { width: 120px; height: 120px; }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <!-- LIQUID GLASS HEADER -->
    <header class="liquid-glass">
        <div class="logo" onclick="app.navigate('landing')">
            <img src="https://uploads.onecompiler.io/42yatf6fu/1781258941988/25088C4A-230C-4E61-8E84-C40FD3A6033C-removebg-preview.png" alt="Nexra Logo">
            Nexra
        </div>
        <nav class="flex gap-4">
            <button class="btn btn-glass" id="btn-header-dashboard" onclick="app.navigate('dashboard')">Dashboard</button>
            <button class="btn btn-primary" id="btn-header-auth" onclick="ui.showModal('auth-modal')">Sign In</button>
        </nav>
    </header>

    <!-- LANDING PAGE -->
    <main id="landing-page" class="view-section active">
        <h1>Studio Quality.<br><span class="text-gradient">Zero Latency.</span></h1>
        <p>The ultimate browser-based screen recording suite. Pure local processing, invisible watermarks, 4K capabilities, and absolute privacy.</p>
        <div class="flex gap-4" style="justify-content: center; margin-top: 20px;">
            <button class="btn btn-primary" style="padding: 16px 40px; font-size: 18px;" onclick="app.navigate('studio')">
                <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="3" fill="currentColor"/></svg>
                Launch Studio
            </button>
        </div>
        <!-- Feature Highlights -->
        <div class="flex gap-4" style="justify-content: center; margin-top: 80px; flex-wrap: wrap;">
            <div class="frosted-panel" style="padding: 24px; width: 250px;">
                <h3 class="text-orange" style="margin-bottom: 10px;">Zero Servers</h3>
                <p style="font-size: 14px; color: var(--text-muted);">All video processing happens on your local GPU. Absolute privacy.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="frosted-panel" style="padding: 24px; width: 250px;">
                <h3 class="text-orange" style="margin-bottom: 10px;">Canvas Burn Engine</h3>
                <p style="font-size: 14px; color: var(--text-muted);">Invisible watermark during recording, securely burned on export.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="frosted-panel" style="padding: 24px; width: 250px;">
                <h3 class="text-orange" style="margin-bottom: 10px;">OBS-Grade Tools</h3>
                <p style="font-size: 14px; color: var(--text-muted);">PiP Camera, Audio Mixing, and Live Annotations in the browser.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </main>

    <!-- DASHBOARD PAGE -->
    <main id="dashboard-page" class="view-section">
        <div class="dashboard-grid">
            <aside class="frosted-panel sidebar">
                <div class="menu-item active" onclick="ui.switchDashTab('home')">
                    <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M3 9l9-7 9 7v11a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2z"/></svg> Home
                </div>
                <div class="menu-item" onclick="ui.switchDashTab('history')">
                    <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M12 2v20M17 5H9.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 0 0 7h5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 0 7H6"/></svg> Local History
                </div>
                <div class="menu-item" onclick="ui.switchDashTab('settings')">
                    <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="3"/><path d="M19.4 15a1.65 1.65 0 0 0 .33 1.82l.06.06a2 2 0 0 1 0 2.83 2 2 0 0 1-2.83 0l-.06-.06a1.65 1.65 0 0 0-1.82-.33 1.65 1.65 0 0 0-1 1.51V21a2 2 0 0 1-2 2 2 2 0 0 1-2-2v-.09A1.65 1.65 0 0 0 9 19.4a1.65 1.65 0 0 0-1.82.33l-.06.06a2 2 0 0 1-2.83 0 2 2 0 0 1 0-2.83l.06-.06a1.65 1.65 0 0 0 .33-1.82 1.65 1.65 0 0 0-1.51-1H3a2 2 0 0 1-2-2 2 2 0 0 1 2-2h.09A1.65 1.65 0 0 0 4.6 9a1.65 1.65 0 0 0-.33-1.82l-.06-.06a2 2 0 0 1 0-2.83 2 2 0 0 1 2.83 0l.06.06a1.65 1.65 0 0 0 1.82.33H9a1.65 1.65 0 0 0 1-1.51V3a2 2 0 0 1 2-2 2 2 0 0 1 2 2v.09a1.65 1.65 0 0 0 1 1.51 1.65 1.65 0 0 0 1.82-.33l.06-.06a2 2 0 0 1 2.83 0 2 2 0 0 1 0 2.83l-.06.06a1.65 1.65 0 0 0-.33 1.82V9a1.65 1.65 0 0 0 1.51 1H21a2 2 0 0 1 2 2 2 2 0 0 1-2 2h-.09a1.65 1.65 0 0 0-1.51 1z"/></svg> Settings
                </div>
            </aside>
            <div class="frosted-panel" style="padding: 32px; overflow-y: auto;">
